social_posts.post_text: Monday night kind of truth bombs 🫶🏼 #LoveBomb wild how it applies to everything no?

Let me start by saying ✨WOW✨! 

Thank YOU! 🫶🏼 What an incredible 7th edition that was! 😍

Your energy, connections & presence made yesterday a dream! This event was a pillar re-launch event for us and we’re so happy to have been able to share a glimpse of what’s to come! 

Our plan is to continue to expand the #LetsConnect community with different big and small (more private) events where our guests will be able to experience something truly unique catered just for them! 😘 #StayTuned

Until then, we’re vibrating high from yesterday! THANK YOU 🤍

We love & appreciate you!
- Mariela and Raquel xoxo
